hadiths[21]{hadithnumber,text}:
4498,"hamein Yahya-bin-Yahya tamimi ne hadis bayan ki, unhon-ne kaha : maine Imam Malik ke samney qirat ki, unhon-ne Rabee-bin-abi Abdur-Rehman se, unhon-ne manbais ke Maula Yazeed se aur unhon-ne Hazrat Zaid-bin-Khalid Johni (Raziallahu anhu) se riwayat ki ke unhon-ne kaha : aik aadmi Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ke paas aaya aur aap se (kisi ki) giri, bhuli cheez ke barey mein malum kya to aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne farmaya : iske dhakney / thaili aur bandhan ki shanaakht kar lo, phir aik saal uski tashheer karo, agar uska Malik aa jaey (to usey de do) warna uska jo chaho karo. usne kaha : gumshuda bakri (ka kya hukm hai?) Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne farmaya : tumhari hai ya tumharey bhai ki hai ya bhediye ki hai. us ne puchha : to gumshuda oont? Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne farmaya : tumhara us se kya talluq hai? uski mashak aur uska moza uske sath hai, wo (khud hi) pani par pahunchta hai aur darakht (ke pattey) khata hai yahan tak ke uska Malik usey pa leta hai. (Yahya ne kaha : mera khayal hai maine ( عفاصها ( padha tha. ( kuchh riwayat mein) وكاءها ( ) iska bandhan ( hai."
4499,"Ismail bin Jafar ne hamein Rabee bin abi Abdur-Rehman se hadis bayan ki, unhon-ne manbais ke Maula (aazad karda ghulam ( Yazeed se aur unhon-ne Hazrat Zaid-bin-Khalid Johni (Raziallahu anhu) se riwayat ki ke aik aadmi ne Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) se ( kisi ki) giri padi cheez ke barey mein malum kya to aap ne farmaya : aik saal iska elaan karo, phir iske bandhan aur thaili wghaira ki shanaakht rakho, phir us se kharch karo, agar iska Malik aa jaey to usey de do. usne kaha : aey Allah ke rasool! gumshuda bakri ? aap ne farmaya : usey pakad lo, wo tumhari hai ya tumharey bhai ki hai ya bhediye ki hai. usne kaha : aey Allah ke rasool! gumshuda oont ? kaha : is par Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ghussey huey yahan tak ke aap ke donon rukhsar surkh ho gaey. padhi. ya aap ka chehra Mubarak surkh ho gaya. phir farmaya : tumhara us se kya talluq? us waqt tak ke uska Malik usey pa ley, uska moza aur uski mashak uske sath hai."
4500,"Abdullah-bin Wahab ne hamein khabar di, kaha : mujhey Sufiyan Sory , Malik-bin-Anas , Amr-bin-Haris aur doosrey logon ne khabar di ke Rabee bin abi Abdur-Rehman ne unhein isi sanad ke sath Malik ki hadis ki tarah hadis bayan ki, albatta unhon-ne ye izafa kya : kaha : aik aadmi Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ke paas aaya to main aap ke sath tha, us ne aap se kisi ki giri-padi cheez ke barey mein puchha aur (ibne- Wahab ne) kaha : Amr ne hadis mein kaha : jab usey talash karne wala koi na aaey to usey kharch kar lo."
4501,"Sulaiman-bin Bilal ne mujhey Rabee bin abi Abdur-Rehman se hadis bayan ki, unhon-ne manbais ke Maula Yazeed se riwayat ki, unhon-ne kaha : maine Hazrat Zaid-bin-Khalid Johni (Raziallahu anhu) se suna, wo keh rahe they : aik aadmi Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ke paas aaya. padhi. iske baad Ismail bin Jafar ki hadis ki tarah bayan kya, magar unhon-ne kaha : to aap ka chehra aur peshani surkh ho gaey aur aap ghussa huey aur unhon-ne us qaul ""phir aik saal uski tashheer karo"" ke baad, ye izafa kya : agar uska Malik na aaya to wo tumharey paas amanat hogi."
4502,"Sulaiman-bin Bilal ne hamein Yahya-bin-Saeed se hadis bayan ki, unhon-ne manbais ke Maula Yazeed se riwayat ki ke unhon-ne Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ke sathi Hazrat Zaid-bin-Khalid Johni (Raziallahu anhu) se suna, wo keh rahe they : Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) se kisi ke girey ya bhooley huey soney aur chandi ke barey mein puchha gaya to Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne farmaya : uski thaili aur) baandhney ki) rassi ki shanaakht kar lo, phir aik saal uski tashheer karo, agar ( kuchh bhi) na jaan paogey to usey kharch kar lo aur wo tumharey paas amanat hogi, agar kisi bhi din uska talab karne wala aa jaey to usey uski adaaeygi kar do. us shakhs ne Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) se gumshuda oont ke barey mein puchha : to Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne farmaya : tumhara us se kya waasta? uska joota aur mishkeeza uske sath hai, wo Malik ke pa leney tak (khud hi) pani par aata aur darakht khata hai. us ne aap se bakri ke barey mein puchha to Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne farmaya : usey pakad lo, wo tumhari hai ya tumharey bhai ki hai ya bhediye ki hai."
4503,"Hammad bin Muslima ne hamein hadis bayan ki, kaha : mujhey Yahya-bin-Saeed aur Rabee raey bin abu Abdur-Rehman ne manbais ke Maula Yazeed se hadis bayan ki, unhon-ne Hazrat Zaid-bin-Khalid Johni (Raziallahu anhu) se riwayat ki ke aik aadmi ne Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) se gumshuda oont ke barey mein poochha. (is riwayat mein) Rabee ne izafa kya : to aap ghussey huey yahan tak ke aap ke donon rukhsar Mubarak surkh ho gaey. padhi. aur unhon-ne unhi ki hadis ki tarah hadis bayan ki aur (aakhir mein) ye izafa kya : agar uska Malik aa jaey aur uski thaili, (andar jo tha uski) tadaad aur uske bandhan ko janta ho to usey de do warna wo tumhari hai."
4504,"mujhey Abdullah-bin Wahab ne khabar di, kaha : mujhey Suhak bin Usman ne abu-Nazar se hadis bayan ki, unhon-ne Basar-bin-Saeed se aur unhon-ne Hazrat Zaid-bin-Khalid Johni (Raziallahu anhu) se riwayat ki, unhon-ne kaha : Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) se ( kisi ki) giri aur bhuli hui cheez ke barey mein puchha gaya to Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne farmaya : aik saal uski tashheer karo, agar uski shanaakht na ho paaey (koi usey apni cheez ki haisiyat se na pehchan sakey ( to uski thaili aur bandhan ki shanaakht kar lo, phir usey khaao (istemal karo), phir agar uska Malik aa jaey to usey uski adaaeygi kar do."
4505,"Abu-Bakar Hanfi ne Suhak bin Usman se isi sanad ke sath hadis bayan ki aur unhon-ne hadis mein kaha : agar usey pehchan liya jaey to ada kar do warna uski thaili , bandhan , (jis ( bartan (main band thi) aur tadaad ki pehchan (mehfooz) rakho."
4506,"Muhammad-bin-Jafar ghandar ne hamein hadis bayan ki, kaha : hamein Shoba ne Salma bin kuheil se hadis bayan ki, unhon-ne kaha : maine Suwed bin Ghafala se suna, unhon-ne kaha : main, Zaid-bin-Sauhaan aur Salmaan-bin-Rabee jihad ke liye nikley, mujhey aik kodaa mila to maine usey utha liya, un donon ne mujh se kaha : usey rehney do. maine kaha : nahi, balke main iska elaan karunga, agar uska Malik aa gaya (to usey de dunga) warna us se fayda uthaaunga. kaha : maine un donon (ki baat manney) se inkar kar diya. jab ham apni jang se wapas huey (to) mere maqdoor main hua ke maine Haj karna hai, chunanche main Madina aaya, Hazrat Ubai-bin-Kab (Raziallahu anhu) se mulaqat ki aur unhein kode ke waqiey aur un donon ki baton se aagah kya to unhon-ne kaha : Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ke ahad mein mujhey aik thaili mili jis mein so Dinar they, main usey lekar Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ke paas aaya to aap ne farmaya : saal bhar uski tashheer karo. maine (doosra saal) uski tashheer ki to mujhey koi shakhs na mila jo usey pehchan paata, main phir aap ke paas aaya to aap ne farmaya : aik saal uski tashheer karo. maine (phir saal bhar) uski tashheer ki to mujhey koi shakhs na mila jo usey pehchan paata, main phir aap ke paas aaya to aap ne farmaya : aik saal uski tashheer karo. maine uski tashheer ki to mujhey koi aisa shakhs na mila jo usey pehchan paata. to aap ne farmaya : uski tadaad, uski thaili aur uske bandhan ko yad rakhna, agar uska Malik aa jaey (to usey de dena) warna us se fayda utha lenaa. phir maine usey istemal kya. (Shoba ne kaha :) iske baad main unhein (Salma bin kuheil ko) Makka mein mila to unhon-ne kaha : mujhey malum nahi (hazrat Ubai (Raziallahu anhu) ne) teen saal (tashheer ki) ya aik saal."
4507,"Behaz ne hamein hadis bayan ki, kaha : hamein Shoba ne hadis bayan ki, kaha : mujhey Salma bin kuheil ne khabar di ya unhon-ne kuchh logon ko khabar di aur main bhi unmein (shamil) tha, unhon-ne kaha : maine Suwed bin Ghafala se suna, unhon-ne kaha : main Zaid-bin Suhaan aur Salmaan-bin-Rabee ke sath (safar par) nikla , mujhey aik koda mila. padhi. unhon-ne usi (pichhli riwayat ( ki tarah us qaul tak hadis bayan ki : phir maine usey istemal kya. Shoba ne kaha : maine das saal baad unse suna, wo keh rahe they : unhon unse suna, wo keh rahe they : unhon-ne aik saal uski tashheer ki thi."
4508,"Qutaiba-bin-Saeed ne kaha : hamein Jarir ne Aamash se hadis bayan ki abu-Bakar-bin-abi-Sheba ne kaha : hamein Wakee ne hadis bayan ki. ibne-Numair ne kaha : hamein mere walid ne hadis bayan ki, Wakee aur Abdullah-bin-Numair ne Sufiyan se riwayat ki Muhammad-bin-Hatim ne kaha : hamein Abdullah-bin-Jafar Raqi ne hadis bayan ki, kaha : hamein Ubaidullah-bin-Umar ne Zaid-bin-abi-Unaisa se hadis bayan ki. Abdur-Rehman bin Bishr ne kaha : hamein Behaz ne hadis bayan ki, kaha : hamein Hammaad-bin-Salma ne hadis bayan ki, un sab (Aamash, Sufiyan, Zaid-bin-abi-Unaisa aur Hammaad-bin-Salma) ne Salma bin kuheil se isi sanad ke sath Shoba ki hadis ki tarah hadis bayan ki. Hammaad-bin-Salma ke siwa, un sab ki hadis mein teen saal hain aur un (Hammad) ki hadis mein 2 ya teen saal hain. Sufiyan , Zaid-bin-abi-Unaisaa aur Hammaad-bin-Salma ki hadis mein hai : agar koi (tumharey paas) aa kar tumhen uski tadaad, thaili aur bandhan ke barey mein bata de to wo usey de do. Wakee ki riwayat mein Sufiyan ne ye izafa kya : warna wo tumharey maal ke tareeqey par hai. aur ibne-Numair ki riwayat mein hai : aur agar nahi (aaya) to us se fayda uthaao."
4509,Hazrat Abdur-Rehman bin Usman Taimi (Raziallahu anhu) se riwayat hai ke Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne haajiyon ki giri padi cheez uthaney se mana farmaya.
4510,"Hazrat Zaid-bin-Khalid Johni (Raziallahu anhu) ne Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) se riwayat ki, aap ne farmaya : jisne ( kisi ke) bhataktey huey janwar ( ontni ( ko apne paas rakh liya hai to wo ( khud ( bhatka hua hai jab tak uski tashheer nahi karta."
4511,"Abdullah-bin-Umar (Raziallahu anhu) se riwayat hai janab Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne farmaya : koi tum mein se doosrey ke janwar ka doodh na dohey magar uski ijazat se. kya tum mein koi ye chahta hai ke uski kothri mein koi aaey aur uska khazana tod kar uske khaney ka ghalla nikal ley jaaey? isi tarah janwaron ke than unke khazaaney hain khaney ke, to koi na dohey kisi ke janwar ka doodh baghair uski ijazat ke."
4512,uper zikr ki gaee hadis is sanad se bhi marwi hai.
4513,"Leis ne Saeed bin abi Saeed se, unhon-ne abu Shureh adwi se riwayat ki, unhon-ne kaha : jab Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne guftgu ki, to mere donon kanon ne suna aur meri donon aankhon ne dekha, aap ne farmaya : jo shakhs Allah aur aakhirat ke din par eman rakhta hai wo apne mehman ko, jo pesh karta hai, usko laaiqe-izzat banaey. sahaba ne puchha : aey Allah ke rasool! usko jo pesh kya jaey, wo kya hai? aap ne farmaya : iske aik din aur aik raat ka ehtimaam aur mehman nawazi teen din hai, jo us se zayed hai wo is par sadqa hai. aur Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne farmaya : jo shakhs Allah aur yaum aakhirat par eman rakhta hai wo achi baat kahey ya khamosh rahe."
4514,"Wakee ne kaha : hamein abdul-hameed bin Jafar ne Saeed bin abi Saeed Maqbari se hadis bayan ki, unhon-ne abu-Shuraih Khuzai (Raziallahu anhu) se riwayat ki, unhon-ne kaha : Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne farmaya : mehman nawazi teen din hai aur khususi ehtimaam aik din aur aik raat ka hai aur kisi musalman aadmi ke liye halal nahi ke wo apne bhai ke yahan (hi) thehra rahe yahan tak ke usey gunah mein mubtala kar de. sahaba ne puchha : aey Allah ke rasool! wo usey gunah mein kaisey mubtala karega? aap ne farmaya : wo iske haan thehra rahe aur uske paas kuchh na ho jis se wo uski mezbaani kar sakey. (to wo ghalat kaam ke zariey se uski mezbaani ka intizam kare.)"
4515,"Abu-Bakar hanfi ne kaha : hamein Abdul-Hameed bin Jafar ne hadis bayan ki, kaha : mujhey Saeed Maqbari ne hadis bayan ki ke unhon-ne abu-Shuraih Khuzai (Raziallahu anhu) se suna, wo keh rahe they : mere donon kanon ne suna aur meri aankh ne dekha aur mere dil ne yad rakha jab Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne ye guftgu farmai. padhi. (aagey) Leis ki hadis ki tarah bayan kya aur is mein ye zikr kya : tum mein se kisi ke liye halal nahi ke apne bhai ke yahan thehra rahe yahan tak ke usey gunah mein daal de. usi ki tarah jis tarah Wakee ki hadis mein hai."
4516,"Hazrat Aqba-bin-Aamir (Raziallahu anhu) se riwayat hai, unhon-ne kaha : ham ne kaha : aey Allah ke rasool! aap hamein kisi (aham kaam ke liye) rawaana kartey hain, ham kuchh logon ke yahan utartey hain to wo hamari mehman nawazi nahi kartey, aap ki raey kya hai? Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne hamein farmaya : agar tum kisi qaum ke yahan utro aur wo tumharey liye aisi cheez ka hukm dein jo mehman ke laaiq hai to qabool kar lo aur agar wo aisa na karein to unse mehman ka itna haq ley lo jo un (ki istitaat ke mutabiq un) ke laaiq ho."
4517,"Hazrat Abu-Saeed Khudri (Raziallahu anhu) se riwayat hai, unhon-ne kaha : ham Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ke sath safar mein they, is beech mein aik aadmi apni sawari par aap ke paas aaya, kaha : phir wo apni nigaah daaein-baaein daudaaney laga to Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne farmaya : jiske paas zarurat se zayed sawari ho, wo uske zariey se aisey shakhs ke sath neki karey jiske paas sawari nahi hai aur jiske paas zarurat se zyada zaade-raah hai wo uske zariey se aisey shakhs ki khairkhaahi karey jiske paas zaade-raah nahi hai. kaha : aap ne maal ki bahut si iqsaam ka zikr kya jis tarah kya, yahan tak ke ham ne khayal kya ke zayed maal par ham mein se kisi ka koi haq nahi hai."
4518,"Ayas bin Salma ne hamein apne walid Hazrat Salma-bin-Akwa (Raziallahu anhu) se hadis bayan ki, unhon-ne kaha : ham Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ke sath aik jang mein nikley, ( rastey mein) tangi ( zaade-raah ki kami (ka shikar ho gaey yahan tak ke ham ne irada kar liya ke apni kuchh sawaariyan zabah kar lein. is par Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne hukm diya to ham ne apna zaade-raah ikattha kar liya. ham ne uske liye chamdey ka dasterkhan bichhaaya to sab logon ka zaade-raah us dasterkhan par ikattha ho gaya. kaha : maine nigah uthai ke andaza kar sakun ke wo kitna hai? to maine andaza lagaya ke wo aik bakri ke baithney ki jagah ke baqadr tha aur ham chaudah so aadmi they. kaha : to ham ne khaya yahan tak ke ham sab sair ho gaey, phir ham ne apne (khuraak ke) thailey ( bhi) bhar liye. uske baad Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne puchha : kya wuzu ke liye pani hai? kaha : to aik aadmi apna aik bartan laya. usmein thoda sa pani tha, us ne wo aik khuley munh waley pyaley mein undela to ham sab ne wuzu kya, ham chaudah so aadmi usey khula istemal kar rahe they. kaha : phir uske baad aath (8) afraad (aur ( aaey, unhon-ne kaha : kya wuzu ke liye pani hai? to Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne farmaya : wuzu ka pani khatm ho chuka."
